author: Been, Hans Nielsen, 1646-1708
title: Vitia dilemmatis illius præcipue, qvo Bias Pirenæus septem Græciæ sapientum unus conjugium sapienti cuique et sapientiæ studioso dissvadere conatus esse memoratur, brevi dissertatione logica (propter ingenium etiam in trita materia pro viribus exercendum)
